    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称“令人震惊”的监狱是英国最紧迫的危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/starmer-says-shocking-prisons-are-the-uk-s-most-urgent-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默表示，解决英国监狱过度拥挤危机是他的主要国内任务，并表示里希·苏纳克领导的保守党留下的公共服务“状况糟糕”，这意味着不受欢迎的决定不可避免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/starmer-says-shocking-prisons-are-the-uk-s-most-urgent-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大计划购买潜艇，距离北约防御目标更近一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/canada-plans-to-buy-submarines-inching-closer-to-nato-defense-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多试图平息盟友的批评，加拿大表示将开始购买潜艇舰队，这可能会增加其国防开支以满足北约的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/canada-plans-to-buy-submarines-inching-closer-to-nato-defense-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 20:36:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
